summary:
Hi, my name is Indy and I am a BSc Sociology graduate at the University of Amsterdam. My hobbies include storytelling through music, writing, and filmmaking. I also have a great interest in sociology and (bio)psychology.

Last year I completed an internship at Nationaal Muziekinstrumenten Fonds (NMF) in order to gain work experience in the cultural sector. NMF is a non-profit organization that contributes to the Dutch music scene by helping talented students and professional musicians find the perfect instrument. I am now working as a marketing assistent for three days a week.
